window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Her toxic past.</b><br> <b>His dangerous future.</b><br> <b>A love worth dying for.</b></p> <p><i>Broken Like You</i> is a gritty, suspenseful stand-alone romance set in the Sinners and Angels Universe. Themes of narcissistic abuse (not from the hero), violence, and love-making. Dual POV. And a happily ever after. Meant for mature audiences.</p> <p><b><i>Author's note</i></b><b>: Previously individually titled </b><b><i>Tortured Sinner</i></b><b> and </b><b><i>Fallen Angel, </i></b><b>published by Tessa James.</b></p>"; 
